column5: I got a johnston 9.9hp that needs a part replaced and a 8 hp sea hawk?   i think... that hasent started in a long while..... can someone point me in the right direction?

Total Marine Services in Scarborough. they have done all the work on my boat and have done a great job.  Eugene has worked on my boat with that old timer service. Ask for Eugene or Oolie. Very good prices as well. Little secret of mine. fast turnaround.
